parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrOp.I’m glad to see you could make it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Wouldn’t miss this for the world, Commissioner Kimura.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Your home is impressive, like a great work of art.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrOp.Thank you. It’s only fitting for a woman of my station.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Sure. I just bought a house myself. It’s not much, but it’s mine and it’s close to the station.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlOp.How nice. I didn’t realize someone in your position could afford a house close to the city.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Well, I had some help finding something affordable.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaOp.You like my suit? It’s brand new.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlOp.You look handsome for such a young man.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlOp.Why, thank you, 1Hero. What’s that you have there?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NPC.I brought some wine. I hope it’s to your taste.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrEx.Let’s head to the dining room, shall we?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp.What did you see, 1Hero? Tell me everything.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Duncan… He’s trying to catch someone called Morgan Deluna… a former Guild thief.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.I was with her… I was trying to protect her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnDe.We’ve got quite a mess on our hands.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrOp.You’re doing perfectly well, 1Hero. Keep up the charm and keep Kimberly close.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.Go to Channel 4 and get ready. I’ll see you there shortly.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Kimberly and Paul seem to be buying the heist story. Do you think there is any truth to it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaDe.Unlikely. My team has a pretty good idea of what's happening. It’s almost over.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Any chance I can know more about what’s going on?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.You’re still on the Guild case, 1Hero. But Melissa is never to know anything about what you do in regards to the Eclipse Guild.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.If Miss Foxx continues to pursue the story, I’ll let the whole world watch her eat cum out of Abraham’s ass.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.I recommend you leave the country while you can.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaDe.1Hero. Nice of you to join us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx^.We’ve gone over all our findings. The Guild connection is undeniable.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.If Wilkes wasn’t a Guild leader, he was at least connected to them closely…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.In my opinion, that whole mansion is nothing but a Guild hideout… taken over by something new.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.Come on. Let’s discuss this in my dining room. I want to know everything.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiWoEx^.I told her everything. We need to break the story.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaEx.I can verify it too… Well… some of it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlDe.Sounds like there are demons under the Wilkes mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiWoEx^.I’m sorry I trespassed on the property, but you must believe me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.Now, now, dear. Let’s sit down and talk for a while.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiBaOp^.Yes, of course. There’s a lot to say.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.You two have been a thorn in my side. You were not supposed to trespass on the Wilkes property.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.It will not happen again and I will make sure of it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.The Guild case is closed and there is nothing more to report.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiAnEx^.But that’s not true! You know that’s not true!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiAnEx^.I won’t keep this a secret! The public must know.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp.Just how much do you want the public knowing?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlAnOp.Hey! Don’t leave me in the dark!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.This has come to an end. I will have no more discussion about the Guild or the mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.I know what you’re thinking, Andrea. But there’s things you don’t know.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnDe.Anything I need to know, I’ll learn on my own.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoEx^.You have to show her, 1Hero… You have to show us both!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.I think it’s best that the two of you leave. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnDe.Well, I’m glad you feel that way, because we’re all fucked.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.There is no Guild here in North Santiva anymore. Duncan is not our man…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeWoEx^.That won’t be easy. He’s being kept in the mansion and it’s not exactly under Guild control right now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnDe.Don’t bullshit me. You can get to him.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Where are you shipping your stuff to, Andrea?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnDe.I’m stepping down and I’m going… somewhere else.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.I suggest you do the same… The both of you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.I’ll pull strings on the way out, but you better hold up your end of the bargain.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.If anything comes back on me, you’re not going to get off either.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.Get out of here, you two. I’ve got a lot of work to do.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NPC.We can’t find the comissioner. She’s disappeared.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NPC.Can you believe this house belongs to the state now? I thought Kimura got off the hook.");
